            <p>MACP (Major Airlines Cancellation Policy) is a customer protection program offered by Travelopick that assures total customer satisfaction with each air ticket purchased. You can now cancel your flight booking within 24 hours from the date of the reservation made.  </p>
            <p>With Travelopick, your trusted travel partner, you can enjoy the benefits of MACP. For the low price of $${macpAmt}, this program allows you to cancel your ticket with a full refund within 24 hours, without any penalty from the date of reservation made. </p>
